---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Card } from '../components/Card';
---

<Layout title="Case Studies — Ansh Bhatt">
  <div class="bg-white">
    <section class="section py-20">
      <div class="container max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6">Case Studies</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#5F5F5F]">
          Real outcomes from real constraints. More coming soon.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container max-w-4xl">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <Card client:load className="bg-[#F6F6F6]">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-[#0B3D2E] uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Series A SaaS Startup</p>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0B0B0B] mb-4">GTM acceleration post-seed</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[#5F5F5F]">
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[#0B0B0B]">Constraint:</span> Unclear product-market fit signals + hiring freeze.
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[#0B0B0B]">Intervention:</span> 6-week diagnostic, customer interview synthesis, revised positioning, hire sequencing plan.
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[#0B0B0B]">Result:</span> 3x pipeline growth in 90 days. Confident next funding story.
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>

          <Card client:load className="bg-[#F6F6F6]">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-[#0B3D2E] uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Fintech Scale-up</p>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0B0B0B] mb-4">Regulatory pathway + ops buildout</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[#5F5F5F]">
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[#0B0B0B]">Constraint:</span> Unclear licensing roadmap. Ops stretched across 3 vendors.
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[#0B0B0B]">Intervention:</span> Legal bench mapped pathway. Ops audit + integration plan. Weekly cadence.
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[#0B0B0B]">Result:</span> License issued in 8 weeks. 30% ops cost reduction.
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section bg-[#F6F6F6]">
      <div class="container max-w-2xl text-center">
        <p class="text-[#5F5F5F] mb-6">Every engagement is custom. Each produces different outputs—but all follow the same framework: clear diagnosis, explicit options, and rigorous execution.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#5F5F5F]">For confidentiality reasons, most case studies stay private. Ask me directly during an initial call.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
